image_analysis.description: A photograph of a coffee station in a kitchen or breakroom area. It features a black and silver Jura espresso machine sitting on a dark grey countertop. On top of the machine is a white plate with a small pastry or tart decorated with red berries. To the left of the machine is a white tray containing white paper cups, plastic lids, and a small white bowl filled with pink and blue sugar/sweetener packets. A stainless steel sink is visible in the lower left corner. Above the counter are white cabinets and a white vertical-slatted window blind or tambour door.
